<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: Classic Start Menu Chaos]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=2349&amp;p=11616#p11616"><![CDATA[
If you set &quot;Pinned Programs folder&quot; to &quot;Use Start Menu folder&quot; then if you drag a folder onto the first column you will get an expandable shortcut to that folder (instead of a plain shortcut).<br /><br />Change the &quot;Small icon size&quot; and &quot;Large icon size&quot; values in the &quot;Menu Look&quot; tab to control the size of the icons.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=2">Ivo</a> — Fri Mar 21, 2014 12:09 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
</entry>
